item.title: About Me
item.dc:creator: janahatilova22
item.content:encoded:
I am currently a student at the Institute of Technology Blanchardstown. I am studying Creative Digital Media. This course has a variety of modules to fit every persons area of interest in digital media which include Web Development, Audio & Video, Graphic Design, Animation, Writing for Digital Media and more . I really enjoy graphic design as well as illustration as I like drawing. I enjoy working on brand strategy assignments, creating posters, doing magazine layouts and creating new characters.
